{"title":"延安小米","authors":["施建石"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":12,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"延安小米"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"施建石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝塔山很高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小米很小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但很养人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑暗持久的年代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粒粒小米，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是颗颗炫目的星星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组成北斗明灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点缀延河夜景。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄土地上淳朴的百姓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用小米丰富的营养，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"养壮了二万五千里征程走瘦了的红军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"供应着共和国的一代伟人……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日历换了一本又一本，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陕北的窑洞成了名胜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小米尽管不一定能上国宴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但已清楚地铸进了学生课本。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每每细读，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都会想到国徽上那束谷穗的根。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，再柔弱的血管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也会奔腾起图强的基因；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，再疲惫的神经，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也当感应到一种精神。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}